  • Constructor Details

    • RmiClient

      public RmiClient(ConnectionInfo connectionInfo) throws RemoteException
      Implements the RMI client functionalities, extending UnicastRemoteObject and implementing VirtualClient and Client. This class handles the connection to the RMI server and processes callbacks from the server.
      Throws:
      RemoteException
